description: From the minds behind games like Bulletstorm and the Vanishing of Ethan Carter comes Witchfire, a game that blends the two while adding in a bunch of new ideas. The game is out now in early access on Steam, but here's why you should consider picking it up if you're looking to scratch the gaming itch.
title: Why You Should Care About Witchfire
